text: Auchay-sur-Vendée is a commune. It is found in the region Pays de la Loire in the Vendée department in the west of France. The municipality was created on 1 January 2017 and consists of the former communes of Auzay (the seat) and Chaix.Arrêté préfectoral 4 August 2016 == Transport == === Road === The D65, D115, D938T and A83 roads pass through the commune. == References == Category:2017 establishments in France Category:Communes in Vendée
title: Auchay-sur-Vendée
